---
description: Rules for product lists, banners, remote images, and UI performance
globs:
  - lib/**/*.dart
---

- Keep list/grid item widgets lightweight and reusable.
- Use cached images for remote catalog content when appropriate.
- Avoid synchronous heavy transforms in build().
- Prefer extracting reusable widgets over large build methods.
- Keep loading, empty, and error states explicit.
- Minimize rebuild scope in lists, sliders, and product cards.
